the amateurs , originally called the moguls , is a 2005 comedy film written and directed by michael traeger and starring jeff bridges .   the story revolves around six friends in a small town in the us who decide to make a full length amateur adult film .   the film was released under the title the moguls in the united kingdom on april 28 , 2006 .   the film was released under the title the amateurs and opened in limited release in the united states on december 7 , 2007 .